data.description: NC location, Encino Forest. Move-in ready 2-story home with 4 bedrooms all upstairs for privacy. Lots of living space in this beauty with 2 living areas and 2 dining areas. Updates include carpet replaced, repainted interior, replaced HVAC 2022, gutters with leaf guards, HardiePlank siding, and energy saving double-hung windows.  Sprinkler system, water softener and refrigerator included. Enjoy Texas barbecues on your expansive backyard deck. Year-round enjoyment at community park and pool across the street. Convenient to major highways, shopping and dining. NEISD schools include Johnson High School.
